INSTALL - Anteater Chess

Requirements:
  GCC 9.0 or later
  GNU Make
  SDL2, SDL2_ttf, SDL2_image

Installing SDL2 dependencies:
  Linux (Ubuntu/Debian):
    sudo apt-get install libsdl2-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev libsdl2-image-dev
  Linux (Fedora/RHEL):
    sudo dnf install SDL2-devel SDL2_ttf-devel SDL2_image-devel
  macOS (Homebrew):
    brew install sdl2 sdl2_ttf sdl2_image

SSH / X11 forwarding (required to display the GUI over SSH):
  Connect with: ssh -X username@server
  Verify X11 is working: echo $DISPLAY  (should not be empty)
  On macOS clients, XQuartz must be installed: https://www.xquartz.org

To build from source:
  tar -xvzf Chess_V1.0_src.tar.gz
  cd Chess_V1.0_src
  make

To run:
  cd bin && ./chess

To run tests:
  make test

To clean build files:
  make clean

To uninstall, just delete the directory:
  rm -rf Chess_V1.0_src/
